














































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































































/* 基础样式 */
.container.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  /* padding: 32rpx; */
  /* background-color: #f5f7fa; */
}
.pv-monitor.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  padding: 10rpx;
  /* background-color: #fff; */
}
.vertical-divider.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  width: 1px;
  height: 40px;
  background-color: #e8e8e8;
  margin: 0 12px;
  align-self: center;
}
.horizontal-divider.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  height: 1px;
  width: 100%;
  background-color: #e8e8e8;
  /* margin: 12px 0; */
}
.stats-box.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  padding: 10px;
  background: #fff;

  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  margin-bottom: 10rpx;
}
.stat-item.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  /* padding: 12px; */
  /* background: #f8f9fa; */
  /* border-radius: 8px; */
}
.stat-content.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 50%
}
.stat-label.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  /* font-weight: 600 */
}
.stat-value.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  font-size: 18px;

  font-weight: bold;
  color: #4488FB;
}
.stat-unit.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-left: 4px;
}
/* 图表区域 */
/* .chart-section {
  margin-bottom: 40rpx;
} */
.chart-card.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  background-color: #ffffff;
  box-shadow: 0 8rpx 32rpx rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  margin-bottom: 10rpx;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.chart-header.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  padding: 12rpx 32rpx;
  border-bottom: 1rpx solid #f0f4ff;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}
.chart-title.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  font-size: 32rpx;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  min-width: -webkit-fit-content;
  min-width: fit-content
}
.chart-tabs.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  display: flex;
  /* gap: 24rpx; */
}
.chart-tab-bar.data-v-5f2965b6 {

  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-around;
  margin-top: 12rpx;
}
.chart-tab-item.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  padding: 12rpx 32rpx;
  margin: 0 2rpx;
  border: 1px solid #4488FB;
  color: #666;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  position: relative;
  width: 120rpx;
  height: 60rpx;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}
.chart-tab-item.active.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4488fb 0%, #6ca2ff 100%);
  color: #fff !important;
  box-shadow: 0 4rpx 12rpx rgba(68, 136, 251, 0.3);
}
/* 时间选择器样式 */
.custom-picker.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  border: unset;
  max-width: -webkit-fit-content;
  max-width: fit-content;
  border-radius: 16rpx;
  /* padding: 16rpx 24rpx;
  margin-top: 20rpx; */
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
}
.chart-body.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  padding: 12rpx;
}
.power-chart.data-v-5f2965b6,
.generation-chart.data-v-5f2965b6 {
  width: 100%;
  height: 480rpx;
}
/* 响应式调整 */
@media screen and (min-width: 768px) {
.stat-grid.data-v-5f2965b6 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
}
.power-chart.data-v-5f2965b6,
  .generation-chart.data-v-5f2965b6 {
    height: 560rpx;
}
}
@media screen and (orientation: landscape) {
.container.data-v-5f2965b6 {
    /* padding: 40rpx; */
}
.stat-grid.data-v-5f2965b6 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
}
.chart-card.data-v-5f2965b6 {
    min-height: 600rpx;
}
.power-chart.data-v-5f2965b6,
  .generation-chart.data-v-5f2965b6 {
    height: 640rpx;
}
}

